snippet.title: EZ Law
snippet.description:
EZ Law is a simple to understand, to-the-point explanation of recent legal decisions in the UK. In each short video, I will explain what has happened in a recent legal case in simple to understand language for those not in the legal industry.

Often, legal cases can affect the lives of everyone. However, due to the inaccessibility of these decisions and the difficult to understand language, often people outside of our industry have no idea what they really mean.

This is where EZ Law comes in. In each video, I shall outline the basic facts of the case, and then briefly explain how the relevant court has come to its decision, as well as the impact this will have on the lives of normal people.
